### AI Meme Generator
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/ai-meme-generator
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Funny Meme",
  "style": {
    "topic": "When the code finally works",
    "template": "Drake Hotline Bling",
    "searchWeb": false
