### ============ Audio Projects ============

### AI Voice Cloner
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/ai-voice-cloner
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Voice Cloner audio",
  "assets": {
    "audio_file_path": "api-assets/id/1234.mp3"
  },
  "style": {
    "prompt": "Hello, this is my cloned voice."
  }
}


### AI Voice Generator
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/ai-voice-generator
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Voice Generator audio",
  "style": {
    "prompt": "Hello, how are you?",
    "voice_name": "Elon Musk"
  }
}


### Get audio details
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/audio-projects/{{audioProjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}


### Delete audio
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/audio-projects/{{audioProjectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
